msgid "Graguz,"
"\n"
"\nI appreciate your enthusiasm for converting potential candidates, but it has come to my attention that the survival rate of your converts is increasingly low. Perhaps a little more patience and a little less ""personal application"" might be more conducive to actually increasing our ranks instead of just thinning the general population. "
