"\nGuthrag's Mask: Last possessed by the Chief's Eye of Fharun Stronghold."
"\n"
"\nFrostbreak Chalice: Rumored to have been reclaimed by one of Urfon's underlings and hidden in one of the fortress's towers."
"\n"
"\nAgra Crun: The blood shield of Malacath's faithful, lost in the wilds of Wrothgar."
"\n"
