#: 21337012-0-2780
msgctxt "21337012-0-2780"
msgid "Father,"
"\n"
"\nI know you will be disappointed, so I am leaving at night, when you aren't around to look upon me."
"\n"
"\nYou know where I have gone. To the new city. I have decided to join the priesthood of Trinimac."
"\n"
"\nYou will blame Sneg, but you should not. I made this decision on my own. If you must know the reason, it is that for a long time I was ashamed to be an Orc. While other peoples grow strong and proud with their great cities—Shornhelm, Stormhaven, Daggerfall, Mournhold, Evermore—we Orcs languish without a home. In Orsinium, I no longer need to be ashamed. "
"\n"
"\nWhenever you find this, and whatever you think of it, I want you to know that I will always love you and that I was never ashamed of you."
"\n"
"\nYour daughter, Sharfum"
