#: 21337012-0-2775
msgctxt "21337012-0-2775"
msgid "I have resolved to leave these pages as a trail to my body. Macabre, I know, but the discoveries I make must be shared with the world!"
"\n"
"\nI am wracked with guilt for unwittingly leading the good Orcs of the quarry to their deaths. But I'm even more ashamed that I feel a little thrill each time I discover something new about this ruin. It is wrong that I should take such pleasure from these explorations, knowing what they have cost?"
"\n"
"\nI suppose it's academic at this point. All that remains is the work. I can't bring the quarry workers back to life, but I can take rubbings and samples from these devices. This ruin is a treasure trove. If only it were less dangerous."
msgstr ""

