"\nI've finally found some work here in Wrothgar. It's not glamorous, but it pays well enough. My boss is a beast-master they call ""Nikolvara the Durzog Trainer."" Quite a mouthful, eh? She's a strange one, I don't mind telling you. Touched I think. But she's a damn fine animal handler. Honestly, I think she likes them better than she likes people."
